ma explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"aa4bdfde-4523-e0ac-ed71-2f61977da1be","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Document"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.documentId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Classify with AI · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"15c66182-ab7a-4577-64da-495f80c6d831","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"e20b7d73-2dc8-0192-0829-9cd42970c7c4","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Classify with AI\n\nLLM classification into: Urgent, Routine, FYI (+fallback). Output port order matches this list.\n\nPorts: ①→ Store as Urgent · ②→ Store as Routine, Capture Failure Context · ③→ Store as FYI · ④→ Alert Slack — Other\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"21047029-1d82-10db-88aa-1052957ebd63","name":"Note: Classify with AI"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Anthropic Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Classify with AI** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 Anthropic API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,1090],"id":"3bfebbee-03bb-f059-8113-f7b1cc3d9560","name":"Note: Anthropic Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as Urgent\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,40],"id":"d44fd1b7-7c9f-f44b-1ddf-710bcf92a53f","name":"Note: Store as Urgent"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as Routine\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,490],"id":"631caeae-d07c-78b0-98e0-b2384060a30e","name":"Note: Store as Routine"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as FYI\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1857,940],"id":"525c36d8-e84d-04eb-2eb0-a346accbfae7","name":"Note: Store as FYI"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Alert Slack — Other\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2181,1390],"id":"c491f38c-3588-b233-9bf3-4f632be11006","name":"Note: Alert Slack — Other"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Reunite Branches\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2829,520],"id":"c53c9d93-644e-2ffe-90c3-651dcd6ef3b4","name":"Note: Reunite Branches"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Airtable)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"b9b47093-b29e-7743-5609-d7b2197bb601","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Airtable)\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"19833c62-832d-5873-4a9a-49f8c063d5f9","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Airtable)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,520],"id":"42db04b5-730b-7610-7269-4bb89a866fc9","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Gmail","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,1540],"id":"459a19a7-b182-8e21-223b-3c5d639e872e","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Gmail\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,1540],"id":"306c263e-0e05-6f5d-0c0c-f9fcb8805c58","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Gmail"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Distill long emails with Airtable and Gmail 24/7\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nDistill long emails with Airtable and Gmail 24/7. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual summarization is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Stamp & Shape Document → Payload Valid? → Classify with AI → Store as Urgent → Reunite Branches → Summarize Run Stats → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating summarization in legal\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Improves response time\n- Standardizes the process every time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; Anthropic API key; Google OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"3df4dd87-b4f8-c3fb-0289-e937b9bd452f","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"6da7f2a9-3a92-773a-aadc-e31879d4b639","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"04e56ece-b53b-ada4-92a2-fbb076707a6d","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-500],"id":"4f767bf2-ff51-990a-109d-9498932799b8","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your summarization process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-500],"id":"4696ad13-899a-84d9-c06f-e91432d3130a","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Document","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Document":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Classify with AI","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Anthropic Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Classify with AI","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Classify with AI":{"main":[[{"node":"Store as Urgent","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Store as Routine","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Store as FYI","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Alert Slack — Other","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as Urgent":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as Routine":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as FYI":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Alert Slack — Other":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Reunite Branches":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Airtable)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Airtable)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Gmail","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"a3b660fe-7c0f-469e-a9a9-2f87efa06941","id":"FDX03888"}